[It is interesting to note that the company pulled the vaccine in
Europe in 2010 but waited to pull the vaccine in New Zealand until
this month. Given the situation with the colostrum, one has to wonder
whether the company has done adequate safety testing on the colostrum
itself. - Mod.TG

The HealthMap/ProMED-mail interactive map of New Zealand is available
at http://healthmap.org/r/00c3. - Mod.SH]
